children.label: isVisible
description: Flag whether the legend should be shown. If there is just a single series, it will be hidden

children.label: position
description: Position of the legend relative to the chart

children.label: showSingleSeries
description: Flag whether the legend should be shown even with just a single series

children.label: isInside
description: Flag whether the legend is inside the chart

children.label: horizontalAlignment
description: Horizontal Alignment of the legend when it is set inside chart

children.label: verticalAlignment
description: Vertical Alignment of the legend when it is set inside chart

children.label: floatingColumns
description: Number of columns when legend is set inside chart

children.label: maxLines
description: Maximum number of lines per legend item

children.label: shouldTruncate
description: Flag whether the legend items are truncated or not

children.label: legendSize
description:
Exact legend width (vertical) or height (horizontal)
Limited to max of 70% of the chart container dimension Vertical legends limited to min of 30% of computed width
